rt failure   Adverse events (rhabdomyolysis, creatinine kinase levels more than 10 times the upper limit of normal values, and liver aminotransferase levels more than three times the upper limit of normal values)    Patient‐perceived quality of life", "rejection_reasons": "", "other_info": ""}
